storyInfo: Estelle meets a new colleague, Tomimi, who is also an Archosauria. She's nervous, but also wants to help the newcomer.

attributes.content: 9:30 P.M. Training Grounds
Thanks for being Bubble's practice partner today.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: It's hard to find someone who can keep the upper hand against her and still have strength to spare.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: And sorry about keeping you so late.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: (Instructor Dobermann is strict in training, but very nice otherwise.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (She's always up until so late at night.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: It's fine, I didn't have anything else anyway.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (It's unbelievable how good Bubble is, given her age.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I wish more people would learn from you.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Are you hungry? It's getting late, so why don't you get something from the cafeteria, and put it on my tab.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Thank you.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: 9:34 P.M. Cafeteria
Heat... How do I heat up food?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Is this the machine?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: It makes a noise, but no heat.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Is it this one?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: There's a little picture of a fire on it. Does it want you to heat the machine with fire?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Put the food in the machine, then light a fire outside... like this, right?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Watch out!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Are you okay?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Why did it explode?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: That's not how you use it.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Good thing you didn't get hurt...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Wait, someone I don't know?!)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (W-What was I thinking? I just reflexively...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Wh-What?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: (And she's an Archosauria too. A new Archosauria colleague?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Excuse me, how do I heat up my food...?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Use this one.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I mean... wait 5 minutes, then press this button.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Don't touch the broken one.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Just put in a maintenance ticket, and someone else will fix it.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Gah, I acted weird again, didn't I?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (The Doctor and Lena wanted me to interact more with others...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I've always used the excuse that it's hard to talk to people who've been here longer than me.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (But this time, she seems new here.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (What do I do now...?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Done already, Estelle?
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Oh...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I guess I forgot about dinner.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Yes... I've eaten.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (She might still be in the cafeteria. I'll go later...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: 9:22 A.M. Convalescent Garden
Feeling relaxed?
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: Mm.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Lena, code name 'Perfumer.')
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I come here at the same time every day for aromatherapy.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (It's how I start my day.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (She smells good, and she's so nice. I wish I had a big sister like her.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: This scent works best on you.
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: It... reminds me of home.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Really?
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: But it's not the scent of a flower... it's a vitamin solution.
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: If you want to talk about your past, I'm here to listen, as is the Doctor.
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: No pressure, though.
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: Thank you.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I know why this scent makes me relaxed... it smells just like the lab I was in when I was little.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (That was before I grew horns.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I lived in a small house. There were many small houses like it in the oval room, each with an Archosauria child living in it.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (They called me a 'failure' and threw me out of the lab.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (The guy who did it was named Danny Chip. He even used to say 'Good morning, my princess' to me through the glass every morning...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Was I abandoned because I'm so unlikeable?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (After that, I lived in the barrens until I joined Rhodes Island.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I don't know what you're thinking about, but this is a time to relax.
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: Mm.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Have you had a proper conversation with anyone lately?
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: I... don't think so...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I don't want to force you, but you could try talking to people you feel comfortable with.
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: All I can do is to help you temporarily relax. You're the only one who can take that step.
attributes.name: Perfumer

attributes.content: I understand. Thank you Lena.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: 2:15 P.M. Medical Department Corridor
I heard we have some new colleagues.
attributes.name: Breeze

attributes.content: Seems like there are new faces every day. Rhodes Island is getting livelier.
attributes.name: Breeze

attributes.content: And the queue at the cafeteria is getting longer too.
attributes.name: Earthspirit

attributes.content: Taking care of the new employees was easier when there were fewer people around. I can hardly even remember their names these days.
attributes.name: Earthspirit

attributes.content: But isn't it your job as a senior member to look after them? Remember how Eyjafjalla used to follow you around like a baby fowlbeast chasing its mother? I think you have a knack for taking care of people.
attributes.name: Breeze

attributes.content: (Joyful cry)
attributes.name: Fowlbeast

attributes.content: Whoa! I didn't mean it literally!
attributes.name: Breeze

attributes.content: Calm down, it's just Estelle's Sir Cromwell.
attributes.name: Earthspirit

attributes.content: I'm sorry!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Earthspirit has horns on her head too, but I guess that's normal for a Caprinae.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Hers are smaller than mine, but much longer.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Would they hit the ceiling if something surprised her in the Doctor's office?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (If I was closer to her, maybe I could talk to her about how to deal with all the problems with having horns.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Is this your pet, Estelle?
attributes.name: Breeze

attributes.content: (Breeze always looks so elegant... I wish I could ask her how to be like that too...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (But Sir Cromwell's not my pet. He's my friend.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (He's the one who found my house and opened the door after I was thrown out of the lab.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (He knows so much more than I do, but he doesn't talk much, and he likes to swear.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: There are a number of support missions scheduled for next week. We'll be counting on you, Estelle.
attributes.name: Breeze

attributes.content: (Breeze is a skilled battlefield medic, so we're often paired together on assignments. Maybe she can sense my discomfort, because she's always so nice and careful around me.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I really appreciate it, but she also feels a little distant... and we hardly ever see each other outside of work.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (The Doctor wants me to take the initiative to talk to her...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I... I'll work hard to bring the patients back...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I couldn't say it. Again.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Sir Cromwell! Don't go! Come back!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: You'll cause trouble for others... and make my coworkers dislike me.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Come to think of it, they were just talking about taking care of new recruits...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: What about that Archosauria I saw yesterday? Does she have anyone to help her?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: She'll get hurt if she's reckless around machines again, like last time.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: But... what can I do? When I'm like... this?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Meaningful crow)
attributes.name: Sir Cromwell

attributes.content: Stop laughing, Sir Cromwell.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Soft humming)
attributes.name: Sir Cromwell

attributes.content: I'm getting treatment and going to the Convalescent Garden every day. But I'm still nervous about meeting others of my kind.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I can see at a glance how different I am from them... so won't they too? Will they think my horns are disgusting?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Short chirping)
attributes.name: Sir Cromwell

attributes.content: Gavial?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Right...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Gavial is an Archosauria too. I see her often at work, but I could never muster the courage to speak to her... I don't know what she thinks of me.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: *Sigh* We're both Archosauria, but she's a great doctor, while I can't seem to do anything right.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Wait! Gavial, I'm not ready yet!
attributes.name: Injured Operator

attributes.content: Wait for what? It'll be over in the blink of an eye.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: The blink of an... arrrggghhh!
attributes.name: Injured Operator

attributes.content: Is she on duty today?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I always hear cries like this when she is.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I wonder what's happening inside...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Curious crow)
attributes.name: Sir Cromwell

attributes.content: Wait, where are you going—
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (It's the girl who almost blew herself up yesterday!)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Huh? You're...
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: (She saw me!)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Wait!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: S-She's strong...
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Oh no!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Are you okay? I'm sorry... I...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Oh, I'm fine!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: You're so strong!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Er... yeah...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Sorry...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: It's okay!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I have to thank you for yesterday. I wouldn't have known how to heat up my food if you hadn't been there.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I just happened to pass by and saw...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I, er, I'm a little busy right now, so—
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Man, my hands are getting sore. Watch over the wounded while I go loosen up my arms a little.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Mm, fresh air!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Huh? Did I just see someone skitter by?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Maybe I'm just tired?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Whew, she almost found us. Good thing there was an empty room here.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I saved you this time, so we're even!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: It'd be bad if Gavial found out.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: W-What do you mean?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: You came to spy on Gavial at work, didn't you?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: (This newcomer seems to have misunderstood... I need to explain, or I'll leave a bad impression on her...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I'm not—
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I came to spy on her too!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Do you know her well?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Er... I guess so...?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I often work with her, but we've barely spoken to each other.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: You like her, don't you?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: (She's a doctor of Rhodes Island. She lives in a different world from someone like me, who's doing odd jobs while receiving treatment.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (When I think of it like that, it's easy enough to convince myself that hiding from her like this is normal.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Well, yes, I think she's amazing.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Then we're friends.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Friends... you want to be friends with me?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: We already know each other, and we both agree Gavial's amazing!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I... guess so...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Then we're friends.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I see.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I made friends with a new recruit...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I should report to the Doctor and Lena.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I didn't do anything in particular, but I'm sure they'll be proud of me.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: My name's Tomimi. What about you?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I'm... Estelle.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Calm down. Keep it friendly by making small talk.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (You can do it.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Is it a code name?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: No, it's my real name.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: It doesn't sound Archosauria.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Um...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: It sounds familiar though.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Is it the Ash Princess?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: You know her?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I heard the story from Inam.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Estelle the Ash Princess was chased out from her castle when bad people took over. But she never gave up, and kept working on her swordsmanship.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: When the time came, she snuck into a party at the castle in a dress, with the help of the loyal Sir Cromwell.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: And at the climax, she put on her armor, caught the sword thrown to her by Sir Cromwell, and completed her revenge.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Some say that she turned to ash once her goal was complete.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Oh no, I started talking and just kept going...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Is it going to put her off? I really should learn to keep my mouth shut...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Wow.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: You really know the story!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I can tell how much you admire her.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Yes... I want to be like her.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (She... doesn't seem so scary.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I wish I could wear a helmet like the princess though.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (They say Rhodes Island has good blacksmiths, but I don't know any of them. Since I don't use weapons in battle, I've never gone to talk to one.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I should muster the courage to go ask them to make me a suit of armor, like the one the princess wore.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: You should practice the sword then.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Yes...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (And learn how to fight using weapons.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Learning from someone who uses a greatsword... Skadi, maybe...? But it's hard to talk to her...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: But why did you run away when you saw me?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Er, it's nothing...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I'm, well, not very confident about my appearance...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Appearance?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Turn around and let me take a look.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: By our standards, it's neither thick or thin... It doesn't really stand out.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: But...
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Doesn't that mean that it's normal?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Really?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I look normal to you?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: But back home, people laughed at me and called me a weirdo because of it...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: They don't understand. Sometimes, it's prettier this way.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Like, take Gavial—
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: (Did Gavial have horns too?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: People like her not just because of how she looks, but because of how strong she is, the way she's invincible in battle.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Oh—ah!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: So you mean I should become strong?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Not quite.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I've thought about it a lot, and I think the reason people like Gavial is because she's Gavial.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I don't understand.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Be yourself. The people who like you will like you. You don't have to make yourself uncomfortable just to get people to like you.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: R-Really?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (That's how another Archosauria sees my horns?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I once read a book called 'One Step from Confidence.' It said that people's tastes change all the time; the important thing is what you think about yourself.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Come find me if you want to borrow it.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Thank you.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: It's really a pain sometimes though. I might accidentally poke the door when I'm going to the Doctor's office, and it's harder to swing a sword like the Ash Princess.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Hm... I guess so.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: But not only does it help you balance, it can also be used as a weapon. That more than makes up for making it a little harder to swing a sword.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: So if you think about it, a tail is very useful.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I see!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (So she was talking about my tail...? I guess she misunderstood what I meant... I like my tail...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (My horns are heavy, but the tail helps me keep my balance.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (It's a good tail.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (But she seems totally unconcerned about my horns... I guess not everyone cares about them... I didn't expect it to be so easy to talk to another Archosauria...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I like you too.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Really?!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Yes. That's why we're friends.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Not as good as Gavial, but like, 0.7 Gavials.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: T-Thank you!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Does she use Gavial as a unit of measurement?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (0.7 Gavials must be high praise.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: So... how many Gavials is the Doctor?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Never thought about it...
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Maybe we can score everyone on Rhodes Island later.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Measured in Gavials?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Mm.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Let's do it!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Oh, looks like Gavial went back.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Let's go spy on her again.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Sorry... I have to get back to work.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Rhodes Island might throw me out if I don't work hard enough...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: What do you do here, Estelle? Are you in the combat squad too?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Where'd that come from?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Is this how friends talk?)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: I am, but I usually work more on the support and rescue side.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Like carrying stuff, moving patients, or evacuating the wounded.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Sometimes I'm also involved in direct combat, like when rescuing the wounded in the heat of battle.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Or escorting our doctors.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Incredible...
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: It's nothing, really...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Just imagine being hurt on the battlefield, surrounded by enemies and at your wit's end, then seeing Estelle dash to the rescue.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: You'd shine so brightly in their eyes. You might even go as high as 0.9 Gavials!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Really?!
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (So even a job like this earns people's respect.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Even better if you deliver them straight to Gavial for treatment.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: 0.9 Gavials plus 1 Gavial is... 8 Gavials...?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Yes, they'll recover even quicker, for sure.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Right. I'll try to send them to Gavial next time then.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: But, er, I really do have to go... it's getting late.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: It was nice chatting with you.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Me too.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I wish I could keep things at 0.9 Gavials.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: 7:23 P.M. Engineering Department
(I never knew making a friend would make me so happy.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Oh? You're still working, Estelle?
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: Um...
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Breeze said there might be dispatch missions next week, so I wanted to load some supplies first.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: There's no overtime pay for this, you know.
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: That's fine.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I often ride in Greypaw's car when I'm on a mission with Breeze.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (The roof's been modified to give more room for supplies, and more importantly, my horns.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I'm less nervous when I'm talking to someone I know.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Kids like you should learn to rest when you can.
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: Otherwise, you'll pay the price when you get older.
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: Just look at all the neck and back pain I get.
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: A few more long-distance trips, and I'd just about break into a thousand pieces.
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: Does it hurt that much?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Yeah.
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: I think I know how to help.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I wonder if Gavial's still on duty.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Really? Hope it works.
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: Wait—
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: 8:20 P.M. Medical Department Corridor
You're back, Estelle.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I just brought a colleague who's not feeling well.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Looks like Gavial's gonna be there for a while longer.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I'm waiting to eat with her.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I'm waiting for Greypaw's treatment to finish.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Wait, it's just a bit of neck pain!
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: Well, since you're here, how about a little massage?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: No! I'm fine! It doesn't hurt at all!
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: Aaaaaaaahhhh––!
attributes.name: Greypaw

attributes.content: Sounds like it's working well.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Is it?
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Forceful treatment always works well.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: That's true.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: What are you smiling about?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Oh, it's nothing.
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I'm glad to have made a friend, and to have helped a colleague.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Even though I still couldn't say it.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (At Rhodes Island, no one laughs at my horns, or scolds me for being clumsy.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (There's still a lot I don't know, but I'm learning every day.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: Oh, looks like they're done.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Hey, Tomimi.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: I made a new friend, Gavial!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Look!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Huh? Where did she go?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Who?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: You're not seeing things, are you?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: (Whew...)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (I ran away again.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: (Looks like I still have a long way to go.)
attributes.name: Estelle

attributes.content: The Archosauria girl sighs, lifts her head, and presses herself against the walls of the clinic, horns and all.
There is no smell of vitamin solution, but she feels surprisingly relaxed.
The dark night and scattered stars outside the windows are no different from what she'd seen out on the barrens for so many years.
Today, however, she is home. Here at Rhodes Island.
